            <levelledPara>
                <title>Training Module Overview</title>
                <para>
                    This training module provides comprehensive guidance on the AMPEL360 Q100 
                    document architecture, including the OPT-IN framework, ATA chapter structure, 
                    lifecycle categories, KNOT/KNU methodology, document numbering conventions, 
                    and repository navigation.
                </para>
                <para>
                    <emphasis emphasisType="em01">Target Audience:</emphasis> New technical 
                    authors, engineers, and documentation contributors joining the Q100 program.
                </para>
                <para>
                    <emphasis emphasisType="em01">Prerequisites:</emphasis> Basic understanding 
                    of aerospace documentation and S1000D concepts.
                </para>
                <para>
                    <emphasis emphasisType="em01">Learning Objectives:</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para>
                    <randomList>
                        <listItem><para>Understand the five-axis OPT-IN framework</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>Navigate ATA chapter structure (00-99)</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>Apply lifecycle categories (LC01-LC13)</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>Use KNOT/KNU methodology for work tracking</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>Follow document numbering conventions</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>Distinguish between SSOT and PUB artifacts</para></listItem>
                    </randomList>
                </para>
            </levelledPara>
            
            <levelledPara>
                <title>OPT-IN Framework Overview</title>
                <para>
                    The OPT-IN framework organizes all Q100 documentation along five orthogonal axes:
                </para>
                <table>
                    <tgroup cols="3">
                        <thead>
                            <row>
                                <entry>Axis</entry>
                                <entry>Stands For</entry>
                                <entry>Purpose</entry>
                            </row>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>O</entry>
                                <entry>Organizations</entry>
                                <entry>Organizational structure and stakeholder areas</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>I</entry>
                                <entry>Interfaces</entry>
                                <entry>System interfaces and integration points</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>N</entry>
                                <entry>Nodes</entry>
                                <entry>Physical locations and installation points</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>T</entry>
                                <entry>Technologies</entry>
                                <entry>Technical systems grouped by ATA chapters</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>P</entry>
                                <entry>Processes</entry>
                                <entry>Business processes and workflows</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                    </tgroup>
                </table>
                <para>
                    <emphasis emphasisType="em01">Example Path:</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para>
                    <verbatimText verbatimStyle="vs11">
OPT-IN_FRAMEWORK/
  T-TECHNOLOGIES_AMEDEOPELLICCIA-ON_BOARD_SYSTEMS/
    E1-PROPULSION/
      ATA_71-POWER_PLANT/
        ATA-71-power-plant/
          71-00-general/
            SSOT/
              LC02_SYSTEM_REQUIREMENTS/
                KNU-71-00-001-REQ-001_fuel-cell-requirements.md
            PUB/
              AMM/
                CSDB/
                  DM/
                    DMC-AMPEL360-71-00-00-00A-001A-A_001-00_EN-US.XML
                    </verbatimText>
                </para>
                <para>
                    This path demonstrates:
                </para>
                <para>
                    <randomList>
                        <listItem><para>T-axis: Technologies (specifically E1-Propulsion)</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>ATA 71: Power Plant chapter</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>SSOT: Single Source of Truth (engineering artifacts)</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>PUB: Publications (derived documentation)</para></listItem>
                        <listItem><para>LC02: Lifecycle category (System Requirements)</para></listItem>
                    </randomList>
                </para>
            </levelledPara>
            
